---
title: Lunchbox with Herbed Ricotta plus Sourdough, Cucumber, Mandarins, Grapes, Nuts & Seeds
description: The mid-day meal becomes a laissez-faire lunch with our nibble-board approach. Lush, herby ricotta is served up with toasty sourdough and crispy-cool cukes for dipping and dunking. Or, layer the toasts with the spread and layer on the cukes and a sprinkle of walnuts, pepitas and sunflower seeds. Sweet grapes and juicy Mandarins on the side add bursts of fresh flavor.
